		(property "Description" "The TPS631000 is a constant frequency peak current mode control buck-boost converter. The device has a 3-A peak current limit (typical) and 1.6-V to 5.5- V input voltage range. The TPS631000 provides a power supply solution for system pre-regulators and voltage stabilizers."
